headline: Qualcomm Announces Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: SAN DIEGO, October 17, 2025--Qualcomm Incorporated (NASDAQ: QCOM) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.89 per common share, payable on December 18, 2025, to stockholders of record at the close of business on December 4, 2025.
